### 获取所有成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据学生ID获取成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/student/STU_001
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据课程ID获取成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/course/COURSE_001
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据学生ID和课程ID获取成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/scores/STU_001/COURSE_001
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加成绩
POST http://localhost:8080/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "STU_TEST",
  "examId": "EXAM_TEST",
  "score": 85.5
}

### 更新成绩
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "STU_TEST",
  "examId": "EXAM_TEST",
  "score": 90.0
}

### 删除成绩
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/scores/STU_TEST/COURSE_TEST
Content-Type: application/json
